messages.text: WHAT? You never say no to slurpees…
BTW, Derek’s having another party this weekend!
Last time I got way too drunk.
Oh yeah, HAHA, you totally blacked out.
Gonna see a movie with Ty and Ben. You in?
Dude, what is going on with you?
If this is about Aidan again, I swear I’m gonna kill you.
So then what is going on?
It was kind of an accident…
Idk, I just wish it didn’t happen.
Oh my god, he’s such a dick. I’m coming over.
So how do you know you’re even pregnant?
This is your body, who cares about Jason!
You need to get over him.
Ya, easy for you to say…
Dude, My heart is beating so fast.
Dude, it sounds like you’re having a panic attack???
Calm down and take a test.
I was too scared to buy one.
I’ll go to the drug store.
Bladder is FULL. Where are you?
Can you also get me some bbq chips?
I don’t know what kind to get?
Regular or pretzel. I hate the peanut ones.
I was talking about the P tests, dummy
Oh, right. Just get the cheapest?
No, we need it to be accurate.
Whatever, just get it and come over.
You close? Really need to pee.
Told me to get on the ground.
And this other customer was trying to help her. And the robbers kept telling him to get on the ground but he didn’t.
One of the guys stabbed him.
They took all the money and left.
This guy is bleeding like a lot.
Sry. We had to go down to the police station.
I never got to buy the tests.
They’re questioning us. Gonna be here a while.
